expert.description:
{Expert Shield}

Shields friendly units on medium area, reducing the amount of damage received from hand-to-hand attacks.

Protection is twice that of Basic Shield.

{Expert Air Shield}

Shields friendly units on medium area, reducing the amount of damage received from ranged attacks.

Protection is twice that of Basic Air Shield.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Protection from Air}

Protects friendly units on small area, reducing damage received from Air spells.

Protection is nearly twice that of Basic Protection from Air.

expert.description:
{Expert Protection from Air}

Protects friendly units on large area, reducing damage received from Air spells.

Protection is nearly twice that of Basic Protection from Air.

