{Expert Bloodlust}

Increases the hand-to-hand damage inflicted by friendly units on medium area.

Effect is twice that of Basic Bloodlust.

{Expert Precision}

Increases the ranged attack damage inflicted by friendly units on medium area.

Effect is twice that of Basic Precision.

{Expert Weakness}

Reduces the attack strength of enemy units on medium area.

Effect is twice that of Basic Weakness.

{Expert Stone Skin}

Increases the defense strength of friendly units on medium area.

Effect is twice that of Basic Stone Skin.

{Expert Prayer}

Bestows a bonus to the attack strength, defense strenght and speed of friendly units on medium area.

Effect is twice that of Basic Prayer.

